    {
      "name": "GET /v1/artists/{artistName} — Get Artist by Name",
      "description": "Retrieves a single artist by their full name (case-insensitive path parameter).\n\n- **200** — Artist found\n- **401** — Missing / invalid credentials\n- **404** — No artist with that name",
